      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_achieve-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～……ほんまに今日はええ一日やなぁ\nコン・サドさんの新刊も無事手に入ったし",
      "startTime": 6.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "他にも、新しい同人誌との出会いが沢山あったわ～\nうちの創作活動にも、ええ刺激になりました",
      "startTime": 15.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "特にコン・サドさんの新刊は……\nうちの心にふかーく刺さりましたわぁ",
      "startTime": 22.0982141614,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "残酷な世界の中、生まれた\n北海道の雪のように、儚い出会い……",
      "startTime": 28.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "そしてあまたの試練を乗り越えていく中\n二人に芽生える強固な友情……",
      "startTime": 36.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "うちが求めてたんは、こういうのやったんです！\n……どうしたんです？　そんな疲れた顔して",
      "startTime": 44.2000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あぁ……優の勢いに圧倒されてな……\nところで、目当ての本は一通り手に入れたんだろ？",
      "startTime": 52.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "はい、おかげさまで。もうたまりません……\nうちの創作意欲が大暴れです！",
      "startTime": 61.0964186987,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あ…はは……同人誌もいいけど、そろそろご飯の時間だ\n実は近くに海鮮丼の名店があるんだ。そこに寄って……",
      "startTime": 70.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるんです、{user}さん\nうちらにそんな所に寄ってる時間なんてありません",
      "startTime": 77.6353291195,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "でも北海道に来たんだし、少しくらいうまい食事を……\n……待ってくれ。「時間がない」って、なんの話だ？",
      "startTime": 86.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "決まってます。これから旅館に戻って新刊の準備です\n言いましたよね？　うちの創作意欲が大暴れやって",
      "startTime": 96.8770716352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "ズバリ、次の新刊のテーマは……『北海道の雪』！\n儚く……そして繊細な友情を描きたいんです",
      "startTime": 107.3437383018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "今この北海道にいる間やないと描けません\nうちのインスピレーションが湧き上がってるうちに！",
      "startTime": 115.8104049685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "今から同人誌を作るのか？　しかも旅行中に……？\n……まぁ、時間の使い方は自由だしな。頑張ってくれ",
      "startTime": 124.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "え？　{user}さん、なんでそんなに\n他人事みたいなこと言うんですか？",
      "startTime": 132.7535135908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "一緒に即売会に行って{user}さんと\n心が繋がり合ったと思ったのに……うち、悲しいです",
      "startTime": 139.2201802574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり……うちにも、うちの趣味にも\n心の中では引いてはるんちゃいます……？",
      "startTime": 150.6868367515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そんな訳ないだろ。優の趣味に恥じるところなんてない\n優のことも、優の趣味も、俺は心から応援してるよ",
      "startTime": 158.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "嬉しい……{user}さんがうちのこと\nそんな風に思ってくれてるなんて",
      "startTime": 167.0740560535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "もし{user}さんが隣にいてくれたら\nうち、最後まで新刊を描き切れる気がします",
      "startTime": 173.3740631743,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、優の創作活動のサポートなら任せてくれ\n応援でもなんでも、出来ることならやらせてもらうよ",
      "startTime": 181.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "本当に、なんでも……？　……よーし、そんなら\n早速旅館に戻りましょ！　沢山手伝ってもらいます",
      "startTime": 191.4333601319,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5766.642920000009,
          "startTime": 197.2000030519
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8189.9762532999885,
          "startTime": 199.6233363852
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "え？　手伝うって、何をだ？　引っ張らないでくれ、優\n……またなのか？　またこの展開なのか！？",
      "startTime": 202.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5864.251168900011,
          "startTime": 208.5309178356
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "はい、{user}さん。この原稿なんやけど\nこことここにベタを塗っといてもらえます？",
      "startTime": 212.59760294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……出来ることならなんでもやる、とは言ったけど\nまさか同人誌作りを手伝うことになるとは……",
      "startTime": 220.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "大体、この原稿用紙もペンも\n一体どこから出てきたんだ……？",
      "startTime": 227.6999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
